org.springframework.social.facebook.api

Class PostData

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.springframework.social.facebook.api.PostData

  • public class PostData
extends Object
    An object that represents a new post to be created. Offers a builder-like way of creating a new post. Given to FeedOperations.post(PostData).
